AD FORMATS

   Velvet Drop – A large take over format which is triggered when a user
   enters the site.
   Video/Image Reveal – A large take over format which is triggered when a
   user hovers over the ad.
   Image Pusher – A large take over format which is triggered when a user
   hovers over the ad. Upon expansion the user can brows through the
   images by moving the mouse over them.
   MORE AD FORMATS

